      <scopecontent id="aspace_c9358359dce9dd6ba933af51be5970d6">
         <head>Content Description</head>
         <p>Diaries, manuscript, in German, Latin, and French, written in the printed editions of Schreib-Kalender.
Accompanied by notes by Jonathan Hill on the cipher and its translation.</p>  
      </scopecontent>
  
